{"tid":1648873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各位和理非去加入銀髮族靜坐","createTime":"2019-10-12T11:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T23:30:32.000Z","uid":269125,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5e61de2067e5dbc0934ac3b236c91a21f66d68","tid":1648873,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"無可否認有人無辦法接受暴力示威，我一位以前既老師不嬲都係黃，但佢認為暴力無辦法接受，慢慢變得唔再join遊行<br />\n但既然係咁，靜坐總得拉掛？<br />\n唔好睇少銀髮族靜坐，甘地咪都係靠坐贏<br />\n<br />\n如果一場和平靜坐而popo武力清場，其實係俾彈葯美國國會落實制裁<br />\n新疆去到集中營先俾制裁，香港呢個level美國會唔會真係啟動制裁好難講<br />\n風險係有，不過班後生係前面又被打又被性侵又被告暴動，去靜坐已經算低風險<br />\n<br />\n如果你無辦法上前綫，無辦法接受武力<br />\n就算今晚過唔到去（我都係），都請聽日朝早，帶齊水同野食，一齊去陪佢地坐，靜靜地咁坐，坐滿狗總門口<br />\n<br />\n和理非，do something。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs. 為保護銀髮族，請參加者唔好主動挑釁狗方。"},{"pid":"26acdde9dd1fe43a7402a20bf3eb2ca76c7548cc","tid":1648873,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"一句野解釋晒點解場運動會輸<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/emwPhS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/emwPhS</a>"},{"pid":"e954da73c022d51b5fb6c909dc0c1b599b8d9fb2","tid":1648873,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <ins> <div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 公民抗爭式交稅<br />\n<br />\n香港人真 &middot; 反抗！！！<br />\n<br />\n入黎跟住做啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n＞【<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669】＜\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669】＜</a></div></ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"bc8b31ca8c5d95db43bc74edb1211a0acbcf9e9c","tid":1648873,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"帶啲嘢過去支持下"},{"pid":"6199b8d4ad2397a47f87962b94cd2e4ce7106fd7","tid