<br />\n<br />\nPs. 為保護銀髮族，請參加者唔好主動挑釁狗方。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:23:01.000Z","msg":"[行動POST] 想要靚畫面？銀髮族48小時靜坐咪就係機會囉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648992</a><br />\n<br />\n警總靜坐現場，有老人有中年人有外國人有後生仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多中年帶哂席同櫈黎，準備過夜。<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">想有新行動？想要靚畫面？咁你就快啲過黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日攰唔出都唔緊要，準備聽日接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我煲大佢，唔好當銀髮手足係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAwXWg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAwXWg8.jpg&h=aab0f8a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89e09d68576a9d2103a9229952ff2a20546641b6","tid":1648873,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"多謝銀髮族"},{"pid":"980fbbe5a6d97b1e83e8c8637963aad6ba2eb64a","tid":1648873,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:36:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45327f8d6c3a6fab9c275ec5bae42ea4d101adef","tid":1648873,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzQhWAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzQhWAi.jpg&h=e252351c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9fa6d24069cac230ceccadceb6923e1dd1c0c34","tid":1648873,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17c534a1a9527f5af2cca09b3845f0f607b197e3","tid":1648873,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":